# 💰 Cash Flow Tracker

A professional personal finance dashboard designed to help users monitor their income and expenditures with real-time analytics and reporting.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Add Salary
- Add Expenses
- Automatic Balance Calculation
- Input Validation and user alerts 

### Level 2
- Data stored using LocalStorage (persists after refresh)
- Delete expenses
- Pie Chart visualization (Chart.js)
- Bar Chart visualization

### Level 3
- Download report as PDF (jsPDF)
- Currency Converter (INR, USD, EUR)
- Budget Alert when balance drops below 10%

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Chart.js
- jsPDF

---

## ▶️ How to Run

1. Open the project folder
2. Open `index.html` in your browser

---

## 📌 Notes

- Data is stored in browser (LocalStorage)
- Works on both desktop and mobile


